      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_004",
      "text": "Friends' Club loot council has first pick on everything that drops in this zone. It's not a rule, it's just how things work when you're the best guild on Erenshor.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_005",
      "text": "Every rare drop on this continent has an FC member's name on it. We just let the rest of you farm so we don't have to.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_006",
      "text": "In Friends' Club we have a saying: if it drops, it's ours. If it doesn't drop, we farm until it does. No guild on Erenshor works harder.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_007",
      "text": "Nice Tattered Leather Tunic, {player}. I vendored mine three weeks ago. I'm wearing Drakescale Cuirass now. But good for you.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_008",
      "text": "I already have three of those. Four if you count the one I'm holding for Azzian. You need it? That's cute.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_009",
      "text": "That drop is reserved for FC members, {player}. We decided before you got here. Actually we decided before you started playing.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_010",
      "text": "Sorry {player}, I don't group with people outside Friends' Club. Nothing personal. Everything personal, actually.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_011",
      "text": "Oh, you want to chat? I'm kind of busy farming Reliquary Hall. You wouldn't understand, it's an FC thing.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Reliquary Hall"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_012",
      "text": "I'd invite you to group but our loot rules are strict and honestly {player}, you'd just slow us down.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_013",
      "text": "You know what the drop rate on Eon, Blade of Time is? I do. I've calculated it across 400 kills. That's the FC difference.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "loot"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_014",
      "text": "Need? NEED? I need EVERYTHING, {player}. It's technically an upgrade for one of my sets. I have seven sets.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "loot"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Liii"
    },
    {
      "id": "liii_015",
      "text": "I know every boss loot pool in Fallen Braxonia by heart. Ask me anything. Actually don't, you'll just waste my farming time.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "loot"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fallen Braxonia"],
