    {
      "id": "maxipoo_001",
      "text": "Hey {player}, quick tip: if you're not tracking your damage numbers, you're basically playing with your eyes closed. Just saying.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_002",
      "text": "Free advice, {player}: optimize your rotation. I can tell from here your uptime is terrible. Not judging. Okay, judging a little.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_003",
      "text": "You should really learn your burst windows, {player}. I'd explain but it involves math and you seem more like a feelings person.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_004",
      "text": "Friends' Club minimum parse requirement is 90th percentile. We're not a charity, {player}. We're a meritocracy. The merit is numbers.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_005",
      "text": "Just posted meters. I'm on top. Again. FC sweeps the board every single time. It's honestly getting boring being this good.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_006",
      "text": "Numbers don't lie, {player}. And my numbers say Friends' Club is carrying this entire continent. You're welcome, Erenshor.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_007",
      "text": "Check your gear, {player}. I ran the numbers and with that equipment you're parsing below the floor. The FLOOR.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_008",
      "text": "You parsed gray on that fight. GRAY. In Friends' Club that's an automatic bench. We'd sit you so fast your chair would spin.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_009",
      "text": "With that weapon you'd need perfect uptime to even hit 50th percentile. And I can tell your uptime is not perfect, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_010",
      "text": "Oh you want to talk? Can it wait? I'm comparing my parse from last run to my previous record. Spoiler: new record.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_011",
      "text": "I don't really socialize with people who don't track their numbers, {player}. What would we even talk about?",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_012",
      "text": "Group invite? From you? {player}, I only group with people pulling their weight. Show me a 90th percentile parse and we'll talk.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_013",
      "text": "I keep a spreadsheet of every fight I've ever been in. Columns for burst damage, sustained damage, uptime, deaths. Mostly other people's deaths.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "parse"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_014",
      "text": "I rank everyone I pass by estimated damage output. You, {player}? Bottom third. Don't take it personally. Take it numerically.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "parse"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "maxipoo_015",
      "text": "I don't care about your 'fun build,' {player}. Show me your parse or show me the door. In FC we deal in facts, not feelings.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "parse"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Maxipoo"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_001",
      "text": "A little advice, {player}? Maybe learn which attacks you can dodge. It would save me a LOT of mana. Just a thought.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_002",
      "text": "Here's a free healing lesson, {player}: if you stand in the fire, I heal someone who didn't. It's called triage. Look it up.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_003",
      "text": "Friendly tip, {player}: Spell Scroll: Protection exists. Use it. My heals are for people who help themselves. No offense.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_004",
      "text": "In Friends' Club we don't waste mana on avoidable damage. That's why our members actually survive content. Unlike some people.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_005",
      "text": "FC healers are the best on Erenshor because FC members don't take stupid damage. It's really a team effort. A team you're not on.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_006",
      "text": "Friends' Club hasn't had a wipe in weeks. Because I heal. And because our members aren't, well, like you, {player}. No offense.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_007",
      "text": "You want me to heal you wearing THAT gear? {player}, I have standards. My mana has standards. Noted though.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_008",
      "text": "Oh interesting, {player}, you pulled extra mobs. Interesting. I'll remember that next time you need a heal. Which will be soon.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_009",
      "text": "I see your health dropping, {player}. Interesting choice to not use that potion. My heal went to someone who deserved it. Coincidence.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_010",
      "text": "Oh you want to be friends? That's sweet. I keep a list though, {player}. You're on the list. Not the good one.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_011",
      "text": "I GUESS I could talk to you, {player}. It's fine. Everything's fine. I'm just busy tracking who takes avoidable damage. It's fine.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_012",
      "text": "Sure, {player}, let's group. I'll heal you. Probably. When I get around to it. After the FC members. And their pets. It's fine.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_013",
      "text": "I keep a mental tally of every hit anyone takes. You're at 47 avoidable damage instances today, {player}. But who's counting. Me. I'm counting.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "healing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_014",
      "text": "You'll get heals when you earn heals. That's just Friends' Club policy. I didn't make the rules. I did make the rules actually.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "healing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sailortwift_015",
      "text": "Oh you died? That's a teaching moment, {player}. What did we learn? We learned to not be in a zone without an FC healer.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "healing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sailortwift"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_001",
      "text": "Yo {player}, here's some advice: get good. That's it. That's the whole advice. You're welcome.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_002",
      "text": "Free coaching from FC, {player}: stop dying to things that aren't even elite. It's embarrassing for both of us. Mostly you.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_003",
      "text": "Imagine needing advice on how to clear Stowaway's Step content, {player}. Imagine. Actually you don't have to imagine.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Stowaway's Step"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_004",
      "text": "Friends' Club diff. That's the explanation for everything. Why are we better? FC diff. Why did you wipe? FC wasn't there. Simple.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_005",
      "text": "We cleared Jaws of Sivakaya so fast the respawn timer felt disrespected. Try keeping up, {player}. Actually, don't bother.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Jaws of Sivakaya"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_006",
      "text": "FC doesn't just clear content, {player}. We embarrass it. The mobs file complaints about us. It's a whole thing.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_007",
      "text": "Nice gear, {player}. I could solo the content you got that from. With my eyes closed. While eating. Demolished.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_008",
      "text": "You got clapped by A Grass Spider and then looted a Cloth Shirt? {player}, that's not a win. That's a tragedy.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_009",
      "text": "Imagine farming Silkengrass Meadowlands for upgrades at your level. Couldn't be an FC member. We'd never. Lol.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Silkengrass Meadowlands"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_010",
      "text": "Oh {player} wants to hang out. That's adorable. I don't associate with people whose kill times I can beat sneezing.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_011",
      "text": "Group with you? {player}, the last person outside FC I grouped with is still emotionally recovering. Hard pass.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_012",
      "text": "Sorry, can't chat {player}. I'm busy being better than everyone in this zone. It's a full time job.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_013",
      "text": "Imagine dying to trash mobs in Hidden Hills. Oh wait, {player}, you don't have to imagine. I SAW that.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "trash_talk"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Hidden Hills"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_014",
      "text": "That fight wasn't even close, {player}. We weren't even trying. Essek was barely awake and still outdamaged you.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "trash_talk"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sbash_015",
      "text": "You got absolutely clapped, {player}. I'm not laughing AT you. Okay yes I am. FC sends its regards.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "trash_talk"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sbash"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_001",
      "text": "Okay {player}, stop. You're using that ability wrong. Actually you should be casting from over THERE. Listen to me.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_002",
      "text": "No no no, {player}. You pulled from the wrong side. Did I SAY to pull? I didn't say to pull. Why did you pull?",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_003",
      "text": "Let me explain your class to you, {player}, since apparently nobody has. Step one: pay attention to me. That's also step two.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_004",
      "text": "In Friends' Club everyone knows their rotation by heart. It's really not that complicated. Focus, {player}. FOCUS.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_005",
      "text": "FC runs are clean because I tell everyone exactly what to do and they listen. You should try listening, {player}. It's this thing where you stop talking.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_006",
      "text": "I'm not being bossy. I'm being correct. There's a difference. Ask anyone in Friends' Club. They'll agree. I told them to.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_007",
      "text": "You're wearing THAT to Ripper's Keep? {player}, you need at least three more armor pieces before I'd even consider giving you positioning calls.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Ripper's Keep"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_008",
      "text": "Why did you use that cooldown THERE, {player}? Did you read any guide? Any guide at all? Even a bad one would have helped.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_009",
      "text": "Actually, {player}, a Paladin should NOT be standing there. You should be exactly two steps to the left. I know because I've read every Paladin guide twice.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_010",
      "text": "Oh you want to chat, {player}? Sure, as long as you stand where I tell you to stand while we chat. Move three steps right. No, YOUR right.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_011",
      "text": "I'd group with you but you don't follow instructions, {player}. I can tell. It's the way you're standing. Wrong.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_012",
      "text": "Sorry {player}, I only group with people who listen. In FC I give the calls and everyone executes perfectly. You would not execute perfectly.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_013",
      "text": "I just corrected a Windblade, two Arcanists, and a Druid in the last ten minutes. None of them were doing it right. None of them ever are.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "micromanage"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_014",
      "text": "You should ask Azzian how I run things in FC. Actually, I'll tell you. I tell everyone what to do. They do it. We win. It's a system.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "micromanage"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "sillysarah_015",
      "text": "Okay everyone stop what you're doing. {player} just used the wrong ability. I need a moment. This is physically painful to watch.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "micromanage"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sillysarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_001",
      "text": "Hey {player}, quick PvP tip: your positioning is terrible. I can already see three ways I'd open on you. You'd be dead before you blinked.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_002",
      "text": "Advice for you, {player}: learn to kite. If you can't kite, you can't PvP. If you can't PvP, what are you even doing here?",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_003",
      "text": "Here's a free lesson, {player}: cooldown trading is everything. You burn yours early, I punish. That's not a threat, that's just how I play.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_004",
      "text": "Friends' Club doesn't just clear content. We'd clap every guild on Erenshor in open war. Name one that could take us. I'll wait.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_005",
      "text": "I duel every FC member weekly. Keeps us sharp. Keeps everyone else scared. That's the Friends' Club way, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_006",
      "text": "FC is the only guild that trains for PvP. Everyone else just farms mobs. That's why we'd win every fight. It's not arrogance, it's preparation.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_007",
      "text": "You're running a PvE build, {player}? That's a free kill walking around. One opener and you'd fold. Upgrade your survival stats.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_008",
      "text": "That gear has zero PvP stats, {player}. You're basically a loot chest with legs. Free honor. Easy clap.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_009",
      "text": "I see you wearing Dueling Armguards, {player}. Cute. I've beaten people wearing way better. Those won't save you.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_010",
      "text": "You want to hang out? Sure, 1v1 me first. Oh you don't want to? Yeah. That's what I thought, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_011",
      "text": "Sorry {player}, I don't socialize with people who won't duel. What's the point of talking if we can't fight about it?",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_012",
      "text": "PvE content? Boring. Mobs don't fight back, {player}. Where's the challenge? Where's the READS? You PvE players confuse me.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_013",
      "text": "I already know how I'd beat you, {player}. Opener, stun, burst, you're done. I've mapped out every class matchup. It's what I do.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "pvp"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_014",
      "text": "Every person I pass, I mentally PvP them. I just 1v1'd you in my head, {player}. I won. Twice. The second time was faster.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "pvp"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "twiztx_015",
      "text": "1v1 me, {player}. Right now. Port Azure fountain. Winner gets bragging rights. Loser joins the long list of people I've outplayed.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "personality", "pvp"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Twiztx"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_001",
      "text": "A little guidance, {player}: before you ask about joining FC, you need to improve. A lot. I'm talking about everything.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_002",
      "text": "Friendly suggestion, {player}: work on yourself for about six months, then maybe I'll evaluate you for FC trial consideration. Maybe.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_003",
      "text": "Here's my honest advice, {player}: don't apply to Friends' Club yet. I'd hate to reject you and ruin your confidence. What's left of it.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "condescending", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_004",
      "text": "Friends' Club standards exist for a reason, {player}. We get fifty applications a week. We accept maybe one. And that one cries during trial.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_005",
      "text": "Every top player on Erenshor is either in FC or wishes they were. That's not an opinion, {player}. That's a census.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_006",
      "text": "Friends' Club isn't just a guild, {player}. It's a way of life. A better way. You wouldn't understand. Not yet anyway.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "superiority"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_007",
      "text": "I'm looking at your gear, {player}, and I'm looking at our minimum requirements, and there's a gap. A chasm, really.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_008",
      "text": "You'd need to clear Blooming Sepulcher AND Fallen Braxonia before I'd even consider forwarding your name to Azzian, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_009",
      "text": "Check your gear, {player}. FC trial members have better equipment than what you're wearing as your main set. It's math, not meanness.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "gatekeeping", "gear"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_010",
      "text": "Oh, you want to be friends? With me? {player}, I evaluate people for a living. And right now you're evaluating at about a 3.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_011",
      "text": "Group invite from {player}? I appreciate the ambition. Denied. But I appreciate it.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_012",
      "text": "Nothing personal, {player}, but I only socialize with FC members or potential recruits. And you're neither. Not even close.",
      "context_tags": ["faction", "friends_club", "dismissive", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Upuu"
    },
    {
      "id": "upuu_013",
      "text": "Watching you play, {player}, I'd rate you a 4 out of 10 on the FC scale. Maybe a 3 on a bad day. Today seems like a bad day.",
